Vijay is a result-oriented DevOps and Cloud Engineer with 12 years of IT experience, including 5.7 years in DevOps engineering. He has strong expertise in cloud platforms (AWS, Azure, GCP), automation, CI/CD, and container orchestration. Vijay has worked extensively with tools like Terraform, Ansible, Jenkins, Docker, and Kubernetes, delivering reliable and scalable cloud solutions.
He is well-versed in Infrastructure as Code (IaC), CI/CD pipeline design, monitoring, and disaster recovery strategies, and has a proven record of collaborating with cross-functional teams to ensure smooth delivery of projects. With a strong networking foundation (TCP/IP, VPNs, Load Balancers), Vijay combines infrastructure knowledge with modern DevOps practices.
He is a self-driven professional with excellent problem-solving, mentoring, and communication skills.

